#

Avocado Toast with Poached Egg

10 min
$3.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

EggGluten (if using regular bread)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option (if using gluten-free bread)

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

BreakfastBrunch

Tags:

QuickHealthyBreakfastBrunch

Description

Creamy avocado spread over crispy toast topped with a perfectly poached egg for a nutritious and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocado: 1
  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • egg: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tsp (optional)
